	\item $G = 1$ numerically, but retains dimension $[G] = [E^{-2}]$
	\item Energy $[E]$ is the fundamental dimension
	\item $\alpha_{\text{EM}} = 1$ by definition (not $1/137$!)
	\item All other quantities expressed in terms of energy
\end{itemize}

